<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Once the file has been saved, it must be moved out of the&nbsp;config/&nbsp;directory and the permissions must be reset, again as a security measure:</p>

<pre>
mv config/config.inc.php .         # move file to current directory
chmod o-rw config.inc.php          # remove world read and write permissions
rm -rf config                      # remove not needed directory
</pre>

<p>Now the file is ready to be used.</p>

<h2>错误及解决</h2>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p>#2002 无法登录 MySQL 服务器</p>

	<p>原因是 /etc/php.ini 中的 mysql.default_socket = /var/mysql/mysql.sock&nbsp;路径和实际 mysql 运行时生成的 /tmp/mysql.sock 不同，所以 php 连接不到 MySQL 服务器。解决办法就是配置 mysql 或者修改 php.ini，两者相同就可以了。</p>
	</li>
</ul>
